      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it\u2019s a total dream. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014kept it tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed it every single weekend. It\u2019s practically in showroom condition, looking just as sharp as the day it rolled off the lot. There might be a tiny, almost invisible stone chip if you look with a magnifying glass, but honestly, you won't find a cleaner ride in the neighborhood. It drives like a cloud and turns heads at every stoplight. I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have!",
